Project Title: Ecommerce Website

Description:
This is a fully functional multi-page ecommerce website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The website allows users to view products, add them to a cart, and proceed to checkout. It features responsive design and interactive cart functionality using JavaScript and localStorage.

Main Features:
- Responsive layout for mobile and desktop
- Product listings on the homepage
- Product detail page with Add to Cart button
- Cart page that updates dynamically
- Checkout form with basic validation
- Persistent cart using localStorage
- Navigation menu across all pages

Technologies Used:
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)
- Git & GitHub
- Github Pages (for deployment)

